# My configs
## Identation
filetype plugin indent on
" show existing tab with 4 spaces width
set tabstop=4
" when indenting with '>', use 4 spaces width
set shiftwidth=4
" On pressing tab, insert 4 spaces
## Other useful configs
set expandtab
set autoindent
set cursorline
set number
syntax on
## Color scheme
packadd! dracula
colorscheme dracula
